    snowkap:caseOutcome "Group mcap loss ₹10.5 lakh Cr peak; dollar bond spreads widened 200 bps; MSCI cut free-float weightings; FPO withdrawn ₹20,000 Cr; SEBI + SC committee probes" ;
    snowkap:caseRecoveryPath "Debt prepayments of $2.65B to reduce promoter pledge below 10%; GQG Partners $3B equity infusion March 2023; mcap partially recovered FY24. Adani Power specifically +80% from trough as Indian power demand surged." ;
    snowkap:caseSource "Hindenburg Research report Jan 2023; SEBI interim order Jun 2023; SC expert committee report May 2023" ;
    snowkap:precedesEventType snowkap:event_esg_rating_change, snowkap:event_regulatory_policy, snowkap:event_fraud_disclosure ;
    snowkap:precedesIndustry "Power/Energy" .

