# =============================================================================
# Phase 14.2 — POSITIVE EVENT PRECEDENTS (8 cases)
#
# Pre-Phase-14 the precedent library was nearly all negative events. When
# the SPARQL query ran for a contract win or capacity addition, it fell
# back to negative cases — producing inappropriate framing like "Vedanta
# Konkola Child Labour" cited as precedent on a Waaree solar auction win.
# Live fuzz audit (2026-04-27) caught this on the ICICI ESG-cert and
# Waaree contract-win articles. These 8 named cases close that gap.
# =============================================================================

